1. FREE PLATFORM LICENSE (GPL-3.0)
   The CLOOMC IDE, simulator, CLOOMC++ compiler, shared abstraction library,
   and CTMM hardware designs are free and open source under the GNU General
   Public License v3.0 for all educational and personal use. This includes:
   - Students of all ages (primary, secondary, university, postgraduate)
   - Parents and families (including homeschool)
   - Teachers and educators
