   Clone it, use it, teach with it, build student projects with it.

2. EDUCATIONAL CURRICULUM PACKAGES (Paid Add-Ons)
   Structured courseware aligned to specific examination boards — including
   UK O-Levels, A-Levels, International Baccalaureate (IB), 11+, GCSE,
   AP, and regional equivalents — are value-added services available for
   purchase separately. These curriculum packages build on the free platform
   but are NOT included in the GPL-3.0 license.

3. COMMERCIAL / INDUSTRIAL LICENSE
   Any use of the platform technology in commercial products, proprietary
   hardware, paid services, or for-profit systems requires a separate
